        <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;color:#7e98a1;text-align:center;margin:10px 0 0;">Six scenarios cycle: border infiltrator · crowd density · highway hazard · litter flag · stealth perch · clear state</p>
