        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;font-size:13px;color:#9fc4ce;line-height:1.65;">
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Stealth class.</b> Sub-audible, sub-radar, sub-visual. Bees aren't seen, heard, or detected by SIGINT.</div>
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Persistence.</b> Perch + harvest energy. Hours of standby per minute of flight. The fleet never leaves station.</div>
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Coverage at scale.</b> 50 million units under one command layer. Continental cordon, city-grid blanket, theatre-level recon — same architecture.</div>
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Edge AGI reasoning.</b> Decisions made on-bee. Bandwidth doesn't gate response time; only verdicts travel upstream.</div>
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Auditable record.</b> Every detection is timestamped, geo-tagged, evidence-grade. Courts, regulators, citizens all get the same log.</div>
          <div><b style="color:#7fe9f5;">Civilian-first ethics.</b> Hard-coded refusal classes — kinetic action against unverified humans, surveillance of private residences without warrant, mass biometric harvest. Encoded in firmware, audited externally.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

